value.name: Walker County Grand Jury indicts nine on meth charges
value.description: The following individuals were indicted by the Walker County Grand Jury on May 6. Earnest Cooper — Possession of a controlled substance - meth (3rd degree felony), tampering/ fabricating physical evidence (3rd degree felony).
